Should I baste the inasal, or no?

00:42:58.254 --> 00:43:00.244
- Yeah, please, please. - With this or this?

00:43:00.244 --> 00:43:02.274
No, always finish with the annatto oil.

00:43:02.274 --> 00:43:03.809
Ah, it's the last.

00:43:03.809 --> 00:43:04.983
Three minutes!

00:43:04.983 --> 00:43:06.479
[3 minutes to go]

00:43:06.479 --> 00:43:10.110
We chop this and then you blanch it in boiling water.

00:43:10.110 --> 00:43:11.622
- Nice, nice. - Okay.

00:43:11.622 --> 00:43:13.775
If there's ice, shock it.

