You were touching this?

00:43:39.956 --> 00:43:42.520
- Okay, just keep going. - Oh my God! My skin!

00:43:42.520 --> 00:43:44.454
No, just keep going, keep going!

00:43:45.701 --> 00:43:48.220
That's really bad.

00:43:48.220 --> 00:43:49.526
- Are you okay? - Can you check on her?

00:43:49.526 --> 00:43:52.074
- What do you need? - No, I just burnt myself really badly.

00:43:52.074 --> 00:43:53.982
- It's okay. - Okay.

00:43:53.982 --> 00:43:56.723
Wait, wait. Ah, okay.

00:43:56.723 --> 00:43:59.002
- Alright. - This is an emergency.

00:44:04.503 --> 00:44:05.609
<i>Ms. Jodi?</i>

00:44:05.609 --> 00:44:07.885
<i>- Where do I put this? Here? - Yes, Chef?</i>

00:44:07.885 --> 00:44:11.627
<i>This is for you, for the front of the house. For good luck.</i>

00:44:11.627 --> 00:44:14.852
<i>- Wow! - I bought this for you guys.</i>

00:44:14.852 --> 00:44:16.743
<i>It's incense.</i>

00:44:16.743 --> 00:44:18.856
<i>The lemongrass smells so good.</i>

00:44:18.856 --> 00:44:22.926
<i>- For good luck, good energy! - It's like we're in a spa.</i>

00:44:23.689 --> 00:44:28.271
<i>Okay. Now, I have a gift for...</i>

00:44:28.271 --> 00:44:31.000
<i>our chef to be.</i>

00:44:33.488 --> 00:44:36.139
