00:44:36.847 --> 00:44:39.476
<i>That's your all-around knife.</i>

00:44:40.628 --> 00:44:42.669
<i>It's personalized!</i>

00:44:42.669 --> 00:44:44.799
<i>My knife says "Super Janella."</i>

00:44:44.799 --> 00:44:48.085
<i>I feel so professional now.</i>

00:44:48.085 --> 00:44:49.648
<i>You feel confident.</i>

00:44:49.648 --> 00:44:51.422
<i>I love it!</i>

